title: The Treehouse Restaurant
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Welsh, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Organic restaurant cafe upstairs from the organic shop serving morning coffee and cake, lunch, and afternoon tea. Has many vegetarian and vegan dishes. Emphasis is on local foods. Caters for evening functions.
